              "title": "识别并起草：",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: inherit\" data-color-scope=\"outer\"><span>一名或多名社区成员识别一项</span><strong><span>行业挑战</span></strong><span>，并在特定</span><strong><span>项目</span></strong><span>或</span><strong><span>工作流</span></strong><span>中，以白皮书、规范或设计等形式起草贡献。</span></span></span></p>"
